default3.3.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultA study into the role of LP Gas to heat rural homes and businesses was carried out by Delta Energy Environment. The resulting report, entitled 
defaultOpportunity for Low Carbon LP Gas in Rural Heating to 2030
default reviewed existing and new heating technologies such as hybrid air source heat pumps, 18 kw LP Gas 
defaultGAHPs
default, fuel cell micro combined heat and power, engine micro combined heat and power, boiler plus solar thermal, boiler plus flue gas heat recovery, and boil
defaulter plus controls. 
