default3.4.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultDelta-ee found that in addition to the 42% energy savings from low-carbon LP Gas technologies, that in old detached properties, LP Gas 
defaultGAHPs
default deliver savings of 3.5 tonnes of CO2 per year. Rural hotels show a savings of 10 tonnes per yea
defaultr.
default&#xa0;
default3.5.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultAccording to Delta-ee 
defaultmodelling for a detached pre-1900 property there are cost saving, as well as carbon saving benefits when using LP Gas. 
defaultRunning cost savings are a high priority for customer decision making LP Gas heat pumps offer a very attractive
default reduction in annual running costs (~£1,200 per year). Hybrid ASHPs &amp; boiler plus controls are quite attractive delivering savings of ~£350 / yr. For other technologies, savings are more modest at &lt;£300 per year.
