defaultGovernment needs to r
defaultecognise the role of a “balanced approach”, and to gain consumer momentum 
defaultfor
default all low carbon alternatives should be included in the UK Policy framework. Government should take positive action to include LP Gas low carbon alternatives in the heat sector to help drive down carbon emissions while supporting the infrastructure transiti
