default4.2.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThrough policies such as the Renewable Heat Incentive and the Green Deal encourage consumers towards pragmatic but efficient solutions. LP Gas is a natural partner to some renewable technologies, and can 
defaulthelp overcome some of the short term barriers for consumer transition. It has an existing supply chain in place as well as an industry which has significant expertise in the unique hard to treat properties found off grid.  
